overfitting (cross-validation, CV) leave-one-out CV k-fold CV caret trainControl() 10-fold CV 10-fold CV 5

# set CV
ctrl <- trainControl(method = "repeatedcv", number = 10, repeats = 5)

caret accuracy kappa performance kappa 

# get best result
getBest <- function(md)
{
  df <- md$results
  index <- best(df, metric = "Kappa", maximize = TRUE)
  best.df <- df[index,]
  return(best.df)
}
